4. Layouts in Android
7
Layout = Structure of UI
Types of Layouts:
1. LinearLayout
Arranges elements vertically or horizontally
2. RelativeLayout
Position relative to other views
3. ConstraintLayout (MOST IMPORTANT)
Flexible, modern layout
Uses constraints
4. FrameLayout
Single view / overlapping views
5. TableLayout
Rows and columns like table

