5. Views and Pickers
Views

Views = UI components (basic building blocks)

Examples:
TextView → displays text
EditText → user input
Button → clickable
ImageView → shows image
CheckBox → multiple selection
RadioButton → single selection
Pickers

Pickers = UI components to select values

Types:
DatePicker
→ Select date
TimePicker
→ Select time
NumberPicker
→ Select number
Spinner
→ Dropdown selection
Quick Viva Summary (VERY IMPORTANT)
Android = Linux-based mobile OS by Google
Framework = Ready-made structure for development
Activity lifecycle = states (onCreate → onDestroy)
Layout = UI structure (Linear, Constraint etc.)
Views = UI elements (Button, TextView)
Pickers = selection tools (Date, Time)
